.000Z","msg":"慘 成龍紅到去歐洲 非洲<br />\n都只可以最多加埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:45:47.000Z","msg":"樓豬都話唔計拍戲果d，以歌手計，最多加埋都好合理姐"},{"pid":"5377fc0fc979ad6fb1eeb89e0a4414513d9eac65","tid":798614,"uid":148473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:50:09.000Z","msg":"羅莽呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64373681140b614caf4b97f983de3255cd4448b","tid":798614,"uid":63057,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2e071c687d8d549a57ee6f0418b9137a08d017e7","tid":798614,"uid":63057,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:26:38.000Z","msg":"認真 王嘉爾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:00:15.000Z","msg":"美國當地時間8 月12日，全美青少年選擇獎（Teen Choice Awards 2018）頒獎禮於洛杉磯正式舉行，歌手<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">王嘉爾以個人</span></span>名義摘得明日之星（Choice Next Big Thing）獎，成為首位獲得該獎項的中國人。<br />\n<br />\n全美青少年選擇獎是由美國福克斯廣播公司組辦的年度頒獎禮，始於1999年，旨在獎勵該年度在音樂、電影、體育、電視以及時尚等領域的傑出貢獻，優勝者由13至19歲的青少年投票選出。<br />\n<br />\n今年6 月，王嘉爾以個人名義入圍該頒獎禮的音樂類單元明日之星獎，成為繼章子怡（2001年最佳女主角提名）、<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成龍</span></span>（2008年最佳動作冒險男演員提名）後<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第三位入選的華人，同時也是首位入圍該獎項的中國歌手</span></span>。據分析，王嘉爾的<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Instagram 粉絲超過1000萬</span></span>，其中<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美國粉絲佔比25%</span></span> ，比重最大，證明了他在美國的高人氣。除了王嘉爾之外，本屆入圍明日之星獎的還有韓國組合Black Pink 、NCT 、Stray Kids，以及美國歌手Jacob Sarto-rius 、Matty B.經過一個多月的投票，王嘉爾最終成為該獎項的獲得者。"},{"pid":"eb0b07f4b974b89a3e7ea0d7f2bf19578e228fd7","tid":798614,"uid":63057,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/220031_cdc679bebbe282e170ab6fe0dca8445e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F220031_cdc679bebbe282e170ab6fe0dca8445e.jpg&h=da62bb09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王嘉爾粉絲男女對半，主要集中在大國、發達國家及地區，25%的粉絲來自美國，20%來自巴西，其次是印度、日本、韓國、中國台灣、意大利、法國、新西蘭、委內瑞拉、中國，主要集中在歐美和亞洲市場。"},{"pid":"573ec62e5742c298e2fd39f004e34ade9b099bd3","tid":798614,"uid":170772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb0b07f4b974b89a3e7ea0d7f2bf19578e228fd7","tid":798614,"uid":63057,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/220031_cdc679bebbe282e170ab6fe0dca8445e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F220031_cdc679bebbe282e170ab6fe0dca8445e.jpg&h=da62bb09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王嘉爾粉絲男女對半，主要集中在大國、發達國家及地區，25%的粉絲來自美國，20%來自巴西，其次是印度、日本、韓國、中國台灣、意大利、法國、新西蘭、委內瑞拉、中國，主要集中在歐美和亞洲市場。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:15:48.000Z","msg":"弱智fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸都用唔撚到ig 個比例梗係低啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098c2e75ce53aa45a43c0df24e4d23fd17366361","tid":798614,"uid":71175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"573ec62e5742c298e2fd39f004e34ade9b099bd3","tid":798614,"uid":170772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb0b07f4b974b89a3e7ea0d7f2bf19578e228fd7","tid":798614,"uid":63057,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/220031_cdc679bebbe282e170ab6fe0dca8445e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F220031_cdc679bebbe282e170ab6fe0dca8445e.jpg&h=da62bb09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王嘉爾粉絲男女對半，主要集中在大國、發達國家及地區，25%的粉絲來自美國，20%來自巴西，其次是印度、日本、韓國、中國台灣、意大利、法國、新西